{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Do not introduce licensing for gamebird shooting",
        "additional_details": "Imposing layers of licensing and further red tape - as the government is exploring - is unnecessary and would be damaging to shooting and conservation. ",
        "background": "We think sustainable game shooting is making a major contribution to nature recovery and rural livelihoods across the UK.",
